"[{\"rowLabel\":\"8 Product 1\",\"item_name[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"delicious Freeze Dried Apple ready snack\",\"product_description[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"Looking for a quick and delicious snack to satisfy your cravings without adding any extra sugars? Our freeze dried apples are the perfect solution! Made from 100% natural apples, our freeze dried snacks are easy to prepare and can be enjoyed anywhere, at any time. We carefully select the ripest apples and freeze dry them to lock in their natural sweetness and crunch. Our freeze dried apples are perfect for on-the-go snacking, hiking, or as a quic\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"EASY PREP — enjoy our crunchy freeze dried apples whenever you need a quick pick-me-up, perfect for on-the-go\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#2.value\":\"DELICIOUS SNACKING — our freeze dried apples are the perfect treat to curb your sweet cravings without any added sugars\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#3.value\":\"WHOLE FOOD NUTRITION — get a taste of the great outdoors in every bite with our nutrient-rich freeze dried apples\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#4.value\":\"EASY TO EAT — no refrigeration required, just tear open and enjoy for a healthy and convenient snack\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#5.value\":\"VARY YOUR SNACKS — pair our freeze dried apples with peanut butter, cheese, or hummus for a tasty and satisfying treat\"},{\"rowLabel\":\"9 Product 2\",\"item_name[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"Freeze Dried Banana Bites - Ready to Eat, Nutrient-Rich Snacks\",\"product_description[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"Snack time just got a whole lot better. Are you tired of bland, unhealthy snack options? Look no furt