ENT SNACKS — Enjoy your favorite black jamun anytime, anywhere with our freeze-dried convenience pack zip\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#2.value\":\"DELICIOUS TASTE — Get the authentic taste of black jamun in a convenient, healthy snack form\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#3.value\":\"LONG-LASTING FRESHNESS — Our freeze-dried snack maintains the flavor and nutrients of fresh black jamun for longer\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#4.value\":\"EASY TO USE — Simply rehydrate the freeze-dried black jamun by soaking it in water or fruit juice\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#5.value\":\"HEALTHY SNACKING — Our black jamun is free of artificial preservatives, colors, and flavors\"},{\"rowLabel\":\"11 Product 4\",\"item_name[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"Freeze Dried Sapota Snack Bites for Healthy On-the-go Moments\",\"product_description[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"Imagine being able to enjoy your favorite fruits anywhere, anytime. The hassle of packing fresh fruits is minimized, and the stress of spoilage is eliminated with our Freeze Dried Sapota Snack Bites. Made from high-quality sapota, these bite-sized treats are perfect for on-the-go moments. We carefully select our materials to ensure our product is free from artificial ingredients and additives, providing you with a guilt-free snacking experience. \",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#1.value\":\"QUICK SNACK SOLUTION - You'll love how easy it is to take these delicious freeze-dried sapota bites anywhere and enjoy them anytime.\",\"bullet_point[marketplace_id=A21TJRUUN4KGV][language_tag=en_IN]#2.value\":\"NATURAL AND ORGANIC - We've carefully selected materials to ensure our product is free from artificial ingredients and additives, providing you with a guilt-free snacking experience.